—ظSarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/stor_delete.mdظ@30b45d5059e367a24fd40704693854d3ffe86856512a211b3d764094b9328757²title: stor delete‘¨ExamplesعDelete a table from the in-memory sqlite database
